---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <title>Prairie Bright Solar – Coming Soon</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <link rel="icon" href="/logo.png" />
  </head>

  <body class="flex min-h-screen flex-col items-center justify-center gap-6 bg-yellow-50 text-green-800 font-sans">
